"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-07-team-gb-star-disrespected-fellow-olympian-explains-nasty-feud-21376127\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB star Josh Kerr believes he was 'disrespected' by a fellow Olympian as he explained his nasty feud with fierce 1500m rival Jakob Ingebrigtsen.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9998357107086292, \"rank\": 0.0001269376875567929, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998850796666, \"rank\": 1.1492027623492154e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 130, \"end\": 148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr clinched a silver medal for Great Britain in the 1500m final at theOlympic GamesinParison Tuesday,missing out on goldto Team USA's Cole Hocker.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 184, \"end\": 197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998653948, \"rank\": 1.3289902061707018e-10, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.992968168483227, \"rank\": 0.003956149680912443, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Norwegian runner Ingebrigtsen failed to make the podium - finishing fourth behind American Yared Nuguse - who walked away with the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9730958405678589, \"rank\": 0.0276438864114924, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 383, \"end\": 391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999593647915321, \"rank\": 3.6921445904751844e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yared Nuguse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the final, Kerr, who ran the race in a British-record time of 3:27.79, was asked about Ingebrigtsen andexplained how the rivalry intensifiedin Budapest last year.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 596, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999364834475297, \"rank\": 6.352058328711376e-05, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Over the years there has been a bit of back and forth,' Kerr toldEurosportwhen asked to 'spill the tea' about his bitter feud with Ingebrigtsen.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 762, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I felt a little bit disrespected last year after my first world title (at the 2023 World Championships in Budapest, Hungary).\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999364834475297, \"rank\": 6.352058328711376e-05, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.8619408158230486, \"rank\": 0.1601651462782807, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There is something about someone saying they are not 100 per cent when you go out and get your first world title that makes it sting a bit.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want everyone to be at their best and I want to beat everyone at their best.\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where it started for me, and I just started being honest with the questions.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was asked and instead of giving everyone the benefit of the doubt, I was being myself without much filter.\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think that annoyed some people and turned some heads.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Running and athletics is a gentleman's sport so there is not a lot of that, but it is what it is.'\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Josh Kerr spills the tea on his rivalry with Jakob Ingebrigtsen \\u00e2\\u0098\\u0095\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u0080#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/3Bq6C5JBn5  Ingebrigtsen, who said he could beat Kerr blindfolded earlier this year, posted about the Briton on Instagram after Tuesday night's race at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9998357107086292, \"rank\": 0.0001269376875567929, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}, {\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Well, I guess he did show up after all\\u2026!'\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ingebrigtsen said about Kerr on his social media account.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Hocker and Nuguse as well\\u2026 My team always say that 'because you have a big mouth and is the one to beat, you have everything to lose in competitions'.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen aimed a massive dig at Josh Kerr in February.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1993, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Ingebrigtsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}, {\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9998357107086292, \"rank\": 0.0001269376875567929, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It is not certain that [Kerr] runs any better now than last year at the same time; he did not run two miles then,' Ingebrigtsen toldTV2in Norway.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6343359595467971, \"rank\": 0.40788654090852217, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I would have beaten him in that race, blindfolded\\u2026 But it's good that people run better than they have done before.'\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Today, Cole Hocker, Yared Nuguse and Josh Kerr outsmarted me.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2334, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cole Hocker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\"}, {\"begin\": 2347, \"end\": 2359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yared Nuguse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\"}, {\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9998357107086292, \"rank\": 0.0001269376875567929, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They were 'the best guys' when it really mattered.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I want to congratulate them all on a great performance!\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, I am disappointed!\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Thank you also to all my competitors for putting on a great show today.\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations to the guys bringing home the medals!'\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Best new mobile games on iOS and Android - August 2024 round-up  ArrowMORE:India wrestler Vinesh Phogat disqualified from Olympic final for being 100g overweight  ArrowMORE:WWE legend sends message to record-breaking Olympic wrestler after historic gold  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\", \"score\": 0.9999798174482639, \"rank\": 2.018290143153693e-05, \"text\": \"Android\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\"}, {\"begin\": 2747, \"end\": 2752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9983946702956876, \"rank\